{"tid":2491013,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人真係好好檢討自己 行到邊都阻住曬","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:46:04.000Z","uid":103799,"like":11,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9f06d7252737233822025a69ec345a50b30e38","tid":2491013,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"我認為要階級制<br />\n1000萬以上身家<br />\n500萬以上<br />\n300萬以上<br />\n100萬或以上<br />\n100萬以下<br />\n<br />\n點樣用階級制好?<br />\n要係身上同車上有個章去分辯<br />\n出街500萬要向1000萬嘅人鞠躬<br />\n就算揸車都要讓路比1000萬人士部車過先<br />\n再落車鞠躬<br />\n坐巴士都要鞠躬同讓位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如此類推<br />\n<br />\n如果無做到高級可以沒收低階級人類嘅資產3萬 如果連3萬都無就要去大西北耕田3個月<br />\n<br />\n咁出街就無咁多人阻住曬<br />\n揸車又小啲人<br />\n又可增加有錢年輕人向上流"},{"pid":"b6ade042a88e4cb185452b667e0bf2281f982278","tid":2491013,"uid":601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔係:<br />\n&lt;1000萬<br />\n1000-5000萬<br />\n5000-1億<br />\n1億+<br />\n咁分"},{"pid":"1b2ad2baa4e98a861e4c9775792cd5a698389f55","tid":2491013,"uid":393515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"精神病去自我隔離 唔好出黎影響人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa8577054fea9033837ef4a295f951f345f05a2","tid":2491013,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ade042a88e4cb185452b667e0bf2281f982278","tid":2491013,"uid":601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔係:<br />\n&lt;1000萬<br />\n1000-5000萬<br />\n5000-1億<br />\n1億+<br />\n咁分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"呢個好d , HK 太多人有 10m up....."},{"pid":"5165e00bf401f40bcd5edbc782aa4bb95fae03cd","tid":2491013,"uid":180251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b6ade042a88e4cb185452b667e0bf2281f982278","tid":2491013,"uid":601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔係:<br />\n&lt;1000萬<br />\n1000-5000萬<br />\n5000